data.description: Welcome home to The Glen at Widefield!  This home has had a fresh coat of paint, is pre-inspected, and is ready to go! Enjoy the perfect balance of peace and convenience!  This home features plenty of space, spanning three levels with five bedrooms, and a five car tandem garage for all your storage needs!  Flexible layout and large bedrooms provide plenty of room for offices, hobbies, or entertaining and hanging out!  Granite countertops are carried throughout the kitchen and bathrooms, and the kitchen boasts a large level island with a gas range, large pantry, and a smart refrigerator, all in stainless steel.  This home faces open space, with serene views, walking trails, ponds, and a neighborhood playground. The main level features a generous flex space, expansive rooms for entertaining and a spacious kitchen, with bedrooms placed on the upper and basement levels. Upstairs, three bedrooms offer personal space, plus a versatile loft, with a full hall bathroom and a laundry room. The primary bedroom offers an en-suite bathroom with a soaking tub and separate shower.  The spacious basement offers plenty of possibilities, from a home gym to additional office space. Take advantage of the raised garden beds in the backyard for your home-grown vegetables and flowers. Located 6 minutes  from Starbucks and Safeway, and 10 minutes from Fort Carson. 14 minutes to the Colorado Springs Airport, and 18 minutes from Peterson Space Force Base.
